text: Vamsi is a given name primarily used by Telugu people. Notable people with the name include the following: ==Given name== *Vamsi Mootha, American scientist *Vamsi Krishna Naidu (born 1982), Indian film screenwriter and director *Vamsi Krishna, Indian film actor ==Surname== *Krishna Vamsi, Indian film director *Vakkantham Vamsi, Indian writer ==See also== *Vamsy Category:Masculine given names
title: Vamsi (name)
